headline: GE HealthCare announces cash dividend for second quarter of 2025
summary: CHICAGO, July 01, 2025--The Board of Directors of GE HealthCare Technologies Inc. (Nasdaq: GEHC) today declared a cash dividend of $0.035 per share of Common Stock for the second quarter of 2025 payable on August 15, 2025 to all shareholders of record as of July 25, 2025.
